---
title: Spinach and Ricotta Ravioli with Creamy Pesto Sauce and Peas
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Spinach and Ricotta Ravioli in just 15 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W39_UK_UQ16463-3_Main_high-7eba8918.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/64bff6bea1aa6db20ea12434.pdf
